   Ford ...................   355,000    283,400   + 25.3
   Chrysler ...............    98,000    131,827   - 25.7
   Nissan .................    27,052     25,965   +  4.2
   Suba-Isu ...............    12,282          0      ...
   Total ..................   907,334    838,106   +  8.3
</TEXT>
